span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">北区部分区域中央空调管道更换&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中标单位：江苏冰洋制冷空调有限公司</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：2.95万元</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">四、</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">主院区净水设备维保及软水机采购安装 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中标单位：盐城市保康净水设备有限公司</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：4.6万元</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">五、</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">净化空调风口过滤棉采购&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中标单位：亭湖区城南王金娣布艺经营部</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：1.78万元</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 2