n; font-size: 20px;\">近3年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">报名截止时间：以具体项目招标活动开始为准。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">联系人：李老师 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;联系电话：0515-88508946</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; text-indent: 2em;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\" href=\"http://localhost/upload/files/2020/2/686728a82346db5e.docx\" title=\"附件：设备维保计划.docx\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">附件：设备维保计划.docx</span></a></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"></span><br /></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2020-02-28\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2020-02-28\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'b90060459f04cb08\',\n  \'views\' => \'585\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844739');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6138','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院2020年医疗设备采购计划公告','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院2020年医疗设备采购计划公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'设备处\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">盐城市第一人民医院2020年医疗设备采购计划经医院党委研究并报主管部门批准，现予以公布（见附件1），欢迎符合条件的供应商报名。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">报名须知：</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">1.<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">仅允许产品生产厂家或取得生产厂家授权期限不少于一年的区域级代理经销商参与本年度设备采购的咨询、调研、招标等活动。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">2.<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">具有独立承担民事责任的能力。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">3.<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">具有履行合同所必须具备的设备和专业知识。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">4.<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">具有良好的商业信誉。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">5.<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">近</span>3<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">6.<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">按要求填写《盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表》（见附件</span>2<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">），并上传医疗器械注册证、医疗器械经营许可证、销售代表授权书、产品销售授权书原件扫描件。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">报名截止时间：以具体项目招标活动开始为准。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">联系人：李老师</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体;\">联系电话：</span>0515-88508946</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\" href=\"http://localhost/upload/files/2020/2/a45a45b6e6cc8949.xls\" title=\"附件1：2020年设备招标公告.xls\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">附件1：2020年设备招标公告.xls</span></a></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\" href=\"http://localhost/upload/files/2020/2/1ac29669fbab4163.docx\" title=\"附件2：盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表.docx\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">附件2：盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表.docx</span></a></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2020-02-26\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2020-02-26\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'