 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">六、本次招标项目联系人：张琳琳</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">0515-88507786</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">附件：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: underline; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: underline; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\" href=\"http://localhost/upload/files/2019/12/6c8027631abd87a8.xls\" title=\"危化品招标目录.xls\">危化品招标目录.xls</a></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px; text-indent: 2em;\"><br /></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">盐城市第一人民医院招标采购中心</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">31</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">日</span></span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-12-31\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-12-31\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'articl