 line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">为体现公开、公平、公正的原则，特此公告三天。如有疑问请与盐城市第一人民医院监察室联系，电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2019年12月27日&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-12-27\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-12-27\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'a0b823c9cb5ba84c\',\n  \'views\' => \'646\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844750');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6156','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院北区6#楼及附房消防主机及部分末端设备更换项目招','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院北区6#楼及附房消防主机及部分末端设备更换项目招标公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'总务处\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">盐城市第一人民医院北区6#楼及附房消防主机及部分末端设备更换项目已具备招标条件，拟对该项目进行公开招标，择优选择施工单位。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、项目概况&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1.1 项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院北区6#楼及附房消防主机及部分末端设备更换项目；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1.2地点：盐城市第一人民医院北区；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1.3招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院北区6#楼及附房消防主机及部分末端设备更换，具体内容详见招标人提供的设计图纸和工程量清单。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1.4发包方式：包工包料。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1.5质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，并通过消防验收合格。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1.6工期：<span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; text-decoration: underline;\">&nbsp; 20 &nbsp;</span>日历天，质保期：不少于2年。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong>2</strong><strong>、投标人资格要求</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">投标人具备独立企业法人资格；</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">投标人须是具有建设主管部门核发的消防设施工程专业承包二级及以上资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证；</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">项目负责人须同时具</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有机电工程专业二级及以上注册建造师资格证书和有效的安全生产考核合格证（B类）。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">3、投标报名</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼810室）投标报名，投标报名时间2019年12月21日8时至2019年12月25日18时。联系人：胡荣艳，0515-68037830；手机：13815581495。逾期不再接收报名。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">4、本项目采用竞争性谈判方式。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">5、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">6、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-66696810。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: right; text-indent: 30px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: right; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 时间：2019年12月20日&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-12-21\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-12-21\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'2ab9766dbb2e6168\',\n  \'views\' => \'380\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844750');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6157','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院医用耗材招标公告','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院医用耗材招标公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'招标采购中心\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">根据《医疗机构医用耗材管理办法》的政策要求，为更好地规范和动态管理医用耗材，经医院领导研究决定，将以江苏省医用耗材阳光采购平台目录为基础，按照“公开、公平、公正”的原则，采用分批次招标采购的方式，对医用耗材进行招标采购，欢迎符合供应商资格要求的企业参加，现将有关事项公告如下：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">一、本次招标采购项目</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">、医用胶片</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">、医用相纸</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">二、供应商资格要求</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">1、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">具备独立法人的资格。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">具有良好的商业信誉。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">3、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">具有独立承担民事责任的能力。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">4、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">具有履行合同所必需的设备和专业技术能力。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">5、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">近三年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">6、参加投标的品种必须入围江苏省药品（医用耗材）阳光采购和综合监管平台。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">三、报名</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">、报名方式：现场报名</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">、报名时间</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">:2019</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">--12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">26</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">日</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">上午：</span>8<span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">：</span>00--11:30&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">下午：</span>13:30--17:00</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">法定假日休息</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">、报名地点：盐城市第一人民医院北区急诊</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">楼招标采购中心办公室（盐城市亭湖区毓龙路</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 19px;\">166</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">号）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">四、报名须知：凡具备资格要求的供应商报名时，须携带企业营业执照副本、资质证书、法定代表人身份证明、平台中标的相关资料、取得生产企业授权的委托书等复印件，上述文件必须加盖单位公章。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">五、我院现有在用已备案产品自动进入候选目录。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、公告公示截止时间：</span>2019<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span>12<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span>26<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">七、本次招标项目联系人：郑蓉</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">联系