style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼810室）投标报名并购买招标文件，投标报名时间2019年 9 月 2 &nbsp;日8时至2019年 9 &nbsp;月 6 &nbsp;日18时。联系人：李纯东、李欣；手机：18796550337、15151002073。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">5. 本项目采用竞争性谈判。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;时间：2019年8月30日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-08-30\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-08-30\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'086a36227e43d3f7\',\n  \'views\' => \'529\',\n  