/p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-08-21\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-08-21\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'cfd4034118e4c126\',\n  \'views\' => \'959\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844770');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6195','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院南区洗衣房洗涤用工服务项目招标公告','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院南区洗衣房洗涤用工服务项目招标公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">1、盐城市第一人民医院南区洗衣房洗涤用工服务已经财政部门批准实施，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2、项目概况与招标内容</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院南区洗衣房洗涤用工服务项目</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院南区（人民南路66号）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.3招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院南区洗衣房洗涤用工服务，用工人数暂定8人，招标人保留调整此次招标规模的权力，投标人需无条件服从。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.4服务期：2年，具体开始时间以招标人通知为准。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">投标人须具有独立法人资格，且为盐城市财政局关于对2017-2019年度盐城市市级小额物业服务及管理项目实行定点采购的通知[盐财购〔2017〕6号]定点采购项目供应商。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">4、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件或授权委托书(注明联系人、联系电话及邮箱)到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼810室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间2019年8月12日8时至2019年8月16日18时。联系人：胡荣艳，0515-68037830；手机：13815581495。 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">5、本项目采用“综合评估法”。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;时间：2019年8月12日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-08-12\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-08-12\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'0b24259e585350f0\',\n  \'views\' => \'618\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844771');
