family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2019年8月7日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-08-07\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-08-07\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'47d8815ca071de98\',\n  \'views\' => \'669\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844772');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6198','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院五官科医院监控系统升级等项目招标公告','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院五官科医院监控系统升级等项目招标公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">1、盐城市第一人民医院五官科医院监控系统升级等项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2、项目概况与招标内容</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院五官科医院监控系统升级等项目。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院五官科医院（南城河路12号）、南区（人民南路66号）、北区（毓龙西路166号)。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.3招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院五官科医院监控系统升级等,具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">投标人须具备电子与智能化工程二级及以上专业承包资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">4、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼810室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间2019年8月1日8时至2019年8月6日18时。联系人：胡荣艳，0515-68037830；手机：13815581495。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">5、本项目采用竞争性谈判方式。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-align: right; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-align: right; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 时间：2019年8月1日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-08-01\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-08-01\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'2147feb7cad7ae6c\',\n  \'views\' => \'769\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844773');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6199','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院南、北区零星维修项目招标公告','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院南、北区零星维修项目招标公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">1、盐城市第一人民医院南、北区零星维修项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2、项目概况与招标内容</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院南、北区零星维修项目。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院南区（人民南路66号）、北区（毓龙西路166号）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.3招标内容：南区冷却塔管道、污水处理站管道除锈粉刷、儿科及呼吸内科雾化室增加电源插座、核医学科和检验科危化品仓库增加防盗门；北区检验科改造、北区支气管镜室改造等维修项目。具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2.4发包方式：包工包料。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">投标人须具有有效的建筑装修装饰工程专业承包二级及以上施工资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">4、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼810室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间2019年8月1日8时至2019年8月6日18时。联系人：胡荣艳，0515-68037830；手机：13815581495。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">5、本项目采用竞争性谈判方式。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;时间：2019年8月1日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2019-08-01\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2019-08-01\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n